## Item #7: zero .js at rest. purge-build-artifacts.cs runs after every
## build to delete the SDK-emitted .js files (worker.js, voice-bridge.js,
## _content/SharedUI/js/wolfs-interop.js). They should never exist on
## disk long enough to be added to git, so no .js entries needed here.
